file.name: elasticsearch.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        json: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes:
    BasicAuth: {scheme: basic, type: http}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Elastic Elasticsearch
  title: Elastic Elasticsearch
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Import records from Elasticsearch
      parameters:
      - description: The Elasticsearch index name
        example: some_index
        in: query
        name: Index
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: The Elasticsearch document type
        example: doc_type
        in: query
        name: Doctype
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: The Elasticsearch query (expects Elastic DSL Query Language);
          defaults to match_all as shown below
        example: '{"query": { "match_all": {} } }'
        in: query
        name: Query
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Number of results to return
        example: ''
        in: body
        name: Size
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Elasticsearch Query
tags:
- {name: SIEM & Log Management}

Error: parse: parse spec: parse operations: paths: tmp0: post: parameters: parse parameter "Size": unsupported parameter type "body"
